[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/10/1010.jpg","floor":"#2","id":"1248264","time":"2017-6-12 15:52","userId":"fireattack","userName":"烈之斩","userSign":"(V1046-R MAHORO)","message":"日文中点“・”（Unicode：U+30FB）是一个只在shift_JIS以及其超集（例如Unicode）里存在的字符，在其他2字节编码，例如GBK或者Latin-1中不存在这个字符，所以会无法识别<br><br>但是我感觉Linux应该是用Unicode存储文件名的，所以不会存在无法识别的问题 至于显示成口那只是你没有字符集全的字体而已，并不影响文件访问<br><br>至于你无法进行文件操作八成是你的Ngnix开的文件服务（？）不支持Unicode或者没开启Unicode功能？<br><br>你试试修改charset试试？或者直接试试别的FTP服务。","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/10/54/105449.jpg","floor":"#2-1","id":"1248274","time":"2017-6-12 16:09","userId":"flyonthesky","userName":"隐世之人","userSign":"","message":"感谢回复。其实Nginx里面是正常的，可以显示的。问题是比如我下载完了这个文件需要删除它的时候，在命令行里使用rm命令删除这个文件就会出现错误，导致无法删除成功=。="},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/10/1010.jpg","floor":"#2-2","id":"1248277","time":"2017-6-12 16:11","userId":"fireattack","userName":"烈之斩","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">风雪桃妆</span> 说: 感谢回复。其实Nginx里面是正常的，可以显示的。问题是比如我下载完了这个文件需要删除它的时候，在命令行里使用rm命令删除这个文件就会出现错误，导致无法删除成功=。=</q></div>那应该是terminal/bash不支持Unicode 你按这个思路搜一搜？<br><br>我随便找了个 <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/12649896/why-doesnt-my-terminal-output-unicode-characters-properly\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">https://stackoverflow.com/questi ... characters-properly</a><br><br>（我linux用得少）"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/10/54/105449.jpg","floor":"#2-3","id":"1248280","time":"2017-6-12 16:13","userId":"flyonthesky","userName":"隐世之人","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">烈之斩</span> 说: 那应该是terminal/bash不支持Unicode 你按这个思路搜一搜？<br><br>我随便找了个 https://stackoverflow.com/questi ... characters-prope...</q></div>我去尝试一下，感谢<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/44.gif\" smileid=\"83\" alt=\"(bgm67)\">。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/28/68/286878.jpg","floor":"#2-4","id":"1248282","time":"2017-6-12 16:15","userId":"yejingchen","userName":"菜叶","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">风雪桃妆</span> 说: 感谢回复。其实Nginx里面是正常的，可以显示的。问题是比如我下载完了这个文件需要删除它的时候，在命令行里使用rm命令删除这个文件就会出现错误，导致无法删除成功=。=</q></div>别光说话不贴代码呀<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/10/54/105449.jpg","floor":"#2-5","id":"1248286","time":"2017-6-12 16:26","userId":"flyonthesky","userName":"隐世之人","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">菜叶</span> 说: 别光说话不贴代码呀</q></div><img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">我错了。<br>错误代码是这个<br>root@ubuntu:/var/www/html/dl# rm (画集・設定資料集)\\ ニーア\\ オートマタ\\ 攻略設 定資料集\\ ≪第243次降下作戦指令書≫.zip<br>-bash: syntax error near unexpected token `画集・設定資料集'"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/28/68/286878.jpg","floor":"#2-6","id":"1248292","time":"2017-6-12 16:33","userId":"yejingchen","userName":"菜叶","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">风雪桃妆</span> 说: 我错了。<br>错误代码是这个<br>root@ubuntu:/var/www/html/dl# rm (画集・設定資料集)\\ ニーア\\ オートマタ\\ 攻略設 定資料集\\ ≪第243次降下作戦指令書≫.zip<br>-...</q></div>你这个是圆括号没有转义导致的吧<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"><br>圆括号在 bash 里是开启子进程运行命令，不过我也不知道为啥语法错误（<br><br>用双引号把文件名 quote 起来吧，具体做法就是打文件名时先敲双引号，然后接着打（这里可以补全），最后括回去就行了"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/17/80/178081.jpg","floor":"#2-7","id":"1248300","time":"2017-6-12 16:44","userId":"ershiwo","userName":"板砖加身","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">风雪桃妆</span> 说: 我错了。<br>错误代码是这个<br>root@ubuntu:/var/www/html/dl# rm (画集・設定資料集)\\ ニーア\\ オートマタ\\ 攻略設 定資料集\\ ≪第243次降下作戦指令書≫.zip<br>-...</q></div>把括号也用“\\”标上。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/10/54/105449.jpg","floor":"#2-8","id":"1248314","time":"2017-6-12 17:18","userId":"flyonthesky","userName":"隐世之人","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">板砖加身</span> 说: 把括号也用“\\”标上。</q></div>嗯试过，然后用加\\的文件名就提示找不到这个文件了=。="},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/10/54/105449.jpg","floor":"#2-9","id":"1248315","time":"2017-6-12 17:18","userId":"flyonthesky","userName":"隐世之人","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">菜叶</span> 说: 你这个是圆括号没有转义导致的吧<br>圆括号在 bash 里是开启子进程运行命令，不过我也不知道为啥语法错误（<br><br>用双引号把文件名 quote 起来吧，具体做法就是打文件名时先敲双引号，然后接着打（这里可以...</q></div>我去试试。谢谢！"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/10/54/105449.jpg","floor":"#2-10","id":"1248331","time":"2017-6-12 18:15","userId":"flyonthesky","userName":"隐世之人","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">板砖加身</span> 说: 把括号也用“\\”标上。</q></div>又试过一遍，然后确实可以通过加\\来转义，之前忘了给空格转义了所以会提示找不到文件，感觉自己ZZ了23333"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/17/80/178081.jpg","floor":"#2-11","id":"1248335","time":"2017-6-12 18:26","userId":"ershiwo","userName":"板砖加身","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">风雪桃妆</span> 说: 又试过一遍，然后确实可以通过加\\来转义，之前忘了给空格转义了所以会提示找不到文件，感觉自己ZZ了23333</q></div>下次打个文件名开头然后用 tab 自动补全（如果没有重名文件的话）。"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/06/12/61238.jpg","floor":"#3","id":"1248307","time":"2017-6-12 17:01","userId":"yuewuying","userName":"asahui","userSign":"(啊呜...)","message":"首先用<br>stat yourfile<br>找到这个文件的 inode，例如37133<br>然后用<br>find . -inum 37133 -exec mv {} new-filename \\;","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/10/54/105449.jpg","floor":"#3-1","id":"1248318","time":"2017-6-12 17:25","userId":"flyonthesky","userName":"隐世之人","userSign":"","message":"在使用stat命令的时候也会提示错误。不过还是感谢，学到了一种方法。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/06/12/61238.jpg","floor":"#3-2","id":"1248323","time":"2017-6-12 17:53","userId":"yuewuying","userName":"asahui","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">风雪桃妆</span> 说: 在使用stat命令的时候也会提示错误。不过还是感谢，学到了一种方法。</q></div>stat -c %i yourfile<br>只显示 indoe，应该不会出错<br>你用 stat --help可以知道"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/10/54/105449.jpg","floor":"#3-3","id":"1248330","time":"2017-6-12 18:13","userId":"flyonthesky","userName":"隐世之人","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">asahui</span> 说: stat -c %i yourfile<br>只显示 indoe，应该不会出错<br>你用 stat --help可以知道</q></div>如果像楼上所说的一样转义之后是可以获取到indoe的，转义之前还不行<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/06/12/61238.jpg","floor":"#3-4","id":"1248334","time":"2017-6-12 18:19","userId":"yuewuying","userName":"asahui","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">风雪桃妆</span> 说: 如果像楼上所说的一样转义之后是可以获取到indoe的，转义之前还不行</q></div>你应该用通配符，例如你的文件 a*.zip，用第一个不是 UTF 的字母，加上后面不是 UTF 的字母，这样 stat看看可以不？或者直接这样 mv 可以吗？"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/10/54/105449.jpg","floor":"#3-5","id":"1248393","time":"2017-6-12 20:08","userId":"flyonthesky","userName":"隐世之人","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">asahui</span> 说: 你应该用通配符，例如你的文件 a*.txt，有第一个不是 UTF 的字母，加上后面不是 UTF 的字母，这样 stat看看可以不？或者直接这样 mv 可以吗？</q></div>果然成功了！居然还有这种操作2333感谢大佬<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/14.gif\" smileid=\"53\" alt=\"(bgm37)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/06/12/61238.jpg","floor":"#3-6","id":"1248399","time":"2017-6-12 20:12","userId":"yuewuying","userName":"asahui","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">风雪桃妆</span> 说: 果然成功了！居然还有这种操作2333感谢大佬</q></div>我觉得还有一个方式，直接装个 zsh + oh my zsh，然后 tab 补全，感觉会帮你转义的全都补全好。因为我一般都是 tab 补全很少打文件名的。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/10/54/105449.jpg","floor":"#3-7","id":"1248402","time":"2017-6-12 20:15","userId":"flyonthesky","userName":"隐世之人","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">asahui</span> 说: 我觉得还有一个方式，直接装个 zsh + oh my zsh，然后 tab 补全，感觉会帮你转义的全都补全好。因为我一般都是 tab 补全很少打文件名的。</q></div>搜噶！原来楼上说的tab自动补全是这么回事。果然要学习的东西还很多呢<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/26.gif\" smileid=\"65\" alt=\"(bgm49)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/20/82/208208.jpg","floor":"#3-8","id":"1248981","time":"2017-6-13 17:41","userId":"aflyhorse","userName":"LunarShaddow🌙","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">风雪桃妆</span> 说: 搜噶！原来楼上说的tab自动补全是这么回事。果然要学习的东西还很多呢</q></div>bash 是 bash-completion 包。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/14/07/140749.jpg","floor":"#3-9","id":"1249000","time":"2017-6-13 17:56","userId":"black_tea2333","userName":"Black_tea","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">风雪桃妆</span> 说: 搜噶！原来楼上说的tab自动补全是这么回事。果然要学习的东西还很多呢</q></div>等等，莫非你是手动把那一长串看着就头疼的文件名在命令行里手打出来的？！<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/10/54/105449.jpg","floor":"#3-10","id":"1249002","time":"2017-6-13 17:58","userId":"flyonthesky","userName":"隐世之人","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Black_tea</span> 说: 等等，莫非你是手动把那一长串看着就头疼的文件名在命令行里手打出来的？！</q></div>不不不<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">复制然后粘贴的。"}]}]